  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tbsp oil in a stone bowl over medium heat until shimmering.",
    "Add the minced garlic and ginger and sauté for 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Add sliced onion, carrot, and bell pepper and stir-fry for 3 minutes until vegetables start to soften.",
    "Add cubed tofu and baby bok choy, stir for another 2 minutes until bok choy is wilted.",
    "Whisk together soy sauce, fish sauce, calamansi juice, vinegar, and brown sugar in a small bowl.",
    "Pour the sauce over the stir-fry, stirring to coat all ingredients evenly.",
    "In a separate small bowl, mix all-purpose flour and rice flour with 2 tbsp water to make a slurry.",
    "Slowly whisk the slurry into the dish, cooking for 2 minutes until the sauce thickens to a glossy consistency.",
    "Sprinkle crushed roasted peanuts and chopped scallions over the finished bowl, then serve immediately from the stone pot."
  ],
